title._content: Chinese Times Grey Cup win headlines VPL 41639

description._content:
DESCRIPTION: Normie Kwong with the Chinese Times - Grey Cup win headlines. The 43rd Grey Cup game was played on November 26, 1955 before 39,417 football fans at Empire Stadium in Vancouver. The Edmonton Eskimos beat Montreal Alouettes by the score of 34 to 19.
VPL Accession Number: 41639
Date: November 26, 1955
Photographer/Studio: Province Newspaper
SUBJECTS: Chinese Canadians, Newspapers, Printers, Printing industry, Football, Grey Cup
Location: British Columbia - Vancouver - 1 East Pender Street
